<br>
<h2 id="1.1">Gordon Ramsay hates him for this...</h2>
<br>
If you want to peel a clove of garlic quickly, put it on a cutting board and firmly press the side of a broad knife against it, until it buckles a bit. Then the skin almost falls off with no frustration or mess. <br>



